        description: "The Enhance Images module helps businesses optimize Google Business Profile (GBP) images using AI. Users can upload business photos, check Google Business Profi",
        searchText: "Enhance Images The Enhance Images module helps businesses optimize Google Business Profile (GBP) images using AI. Users can upload business photos, check Google Business Profile compliance, improve image quality, and generate SEO-friendly image metadata to enhance their local search presence. Upload Images Users can upload one or multiple business images for analysis and enhancement. Supported Formats JPG JPEG PNG WEBP Upload Limits Maximum file size: 5 MB per image Multiple image uploads supported. Users can: Drag and drop images. Browse and upload images manually. AI Enhancement Usage The platform displays monthly image enhancement usage. It shows: Total AI enhancements used Remaining enhancements available for the current month This helps users track their image enhancement limits. Image Quality Analysis Each uploaded image is analyzed and assigned an Overall Quality Score. The score is calculated using several quality factors, including: Resolution Brightness Sharpness Google Business Profile compliance A higher score indicates better image quality and optimization potential. Quality Metrics The platform evaluates the following image quality metrics. Resolution Measures the image dimensions and clarity. Higher-resolution images generally provide a better user experience. Brightness Measures the lighting quality of the image. Well-lit images improve visual appeal and engagement. Sharpness Measures the image's level of detail and clarity. Low sharpness may indicate blurry or low-quality images. GBP Compliance Measures whether the image meets Google Business Profile image recommendations. The analysis verifies: Recommended image dimensions Supported file formats File size limitations Image quality standards GBP Compliance Analysis The module checks whether uploaded images comply with Google Business Profile requirements. The analysis includes: Image resolution validation File size validation Format validation Quality recommendations The platform also provides recommendations for improving non-compliant images. Image Recommendations AI-generated recommendations are provided to improve image quality and compliance. Recommendations may include: Improving lighting Increasing image clarity Enhancing sharpness Adjusting image quality Replacing low-quality images Before & After Comparison The module provides a comparison interface between: Original Image Enhanced Image Users can visually compare improvements before applying changes. Describe Your Changes Users can provide custom instructions to the AI describing how the image should be enhanced. Examples include: Improve lighting Remove unwanted objects Increase clarity Enhance image quality Improve colors Implement Change The Implement Change button applies the requested AI enhancements to the image. The platform processes the image and generates an updated version while maintaining a natural appearance. Download Enhanced Image Enhanced images can be downloaded in multiple formats: JPG PNG WEBP This allows users to use the optimized images across various platforms. Image SEO Suggestions The platform automatically generates SEO recommendations for uploaded images. The suggestions include: Filename An SEO-friendly image filename optimized for search visibility. Alt Text AI-generated descriptive alt text to improve accessibility and image discoverability. Category Automatically categorizes the image based on its content. Examples include: Products Interior Exterior Team Food Services Additional Image Metrics The module also displays: Brightness Score Sharpness Score Contrast Score Clarity Score These metrics help users better understand the overall image quality. Enhance All The Enhance All option allows users to apply AI enhancements to all uploaded images simultaneously. This helps businesses optimize multiple images quickly and efficiently.",
