        description: "The Sent Emails module provides a centralized view of all outreach emails sent through Blazly Backlink Finder. It allows users to monitor email campaigns, revie",
        searchText: "Sent Emails The Sent Emails module provides a centralized view of all outreach emails sent through Blazly Backlink Finder. It allows users to monitor email campaigns, review message content, and track outreach history in one place. This module serves as an outreach activity log, helping users keep track of all communications sent to backlink prospects and publishers. Each email record contains detailed information about the outreach message. Sent Time Displays the exact date and time the email was sent. Example: Mon, Jun 15, 2026, 5:44 PM This helps users track campaign activity and outreach timelines. Email Subject Displays the subject line used in the outreach email. Example: Powerful SEO Tools: Blazly AI The subject line is designed to improve email open rates and increase engagement. Recipient Displays the email address of the recipient. Example: brandonabbott@youtube.com This identifies who received the outreach message. Campaign Target Displays the webpage or content that the outreach email references. Example: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16mFGnOBF0k The campaign target helps users understand the context of the outreach and the content being referenced. Message Body Displays the complete email content that was sent to the recipient. The message body may include: Personalized introduction Context about the recipient's content Product or website introduction Outreach request Resource recommendation Call-to-action Campaign Label Emails associated with campaigns are tagged with a Campaign badge, allowing users to quickly identify campaign-related outreach messages. Sent Email Workflow Generate Outreach Email ↓ Send Email ↓ Store Email History ↓ Track Sent Messages ↓ Review Outreach Performance Use Cases Campaign Monitoring Track all emails sent for backlink outreach campaigns. Outreach Auditing Review previously sent messages and verify communication details. Team Collaboration Allow team members to view sent outreach history and avoid duplicate contacts. Performance Analysis Use sent email history to evaluate outreach strategies and improve future campaigns.",
