        title: "Email Integration",
        description: "The Email Integration module allows users to connect their email accounts to Blazly Backlink Finder for sending outreach campaigns, tracking email opens, and ma",
        searchText: "Email Integration The Email Integration module allows users to connect their email accounts to Blazly Backlink Finder for sending outreach campaigns, tracking email opens, and managing replies. Blazly supports two integration method: 1. Gmail (OAuth) Gmail (OAuth) The Gmail integration allows users to securely connect their Google account without manually configuring email server settings. How Gmail OAuth Works Step 1: Connect Gmail Click Connect Gmail and sign in using your Google account. Step 2: Grant Permissions Google requests permission to: Send emails Read mail (read-only) These permissions allow Blazly to: Send outreach emails Display reply previews Synchronize email activity Step 3: Secure Authentication After approval: A secure authentication token is stored. Emails are sent using the Gmail API. No Gmail password is stored by Blazly. Step 4: Send Campaign Emails Once connected, all outreach emails are sent directly from your Gmail account. Email activity automatically appears in: Dashboard metrics Sent Emails Email Replies Gmail Connection Status The integration page displays the current Gmail connection status. Available actions: Connect Gmail Disconnect Gmail Reconnect Gmail Pricing Pricing The Pricing page allows users to compare available subscription plans and upgrade based on their outreach requirements. Each plan provides different limits for campaigns, backlink opportunities, email sending, and advanced automation features. Blazly Backlink Finder currently offers three subscription plans: Starter Growth Scale Starter Plan Price: $29/month Best for: Beginners testing outreach campaigns and backlink building. Features 1 Active Campaign Find up to 50 backlink opportunities per month AI Website Qualification AI Verified Email Finder Send up to 50 outreach emails per month AI Personalized Email Generation Export outreach data as CSV (manual send) Action Choose Starter Growth Plan Price: $99/month Best for: Businesses and marketers running multiple outreach campaigns. Features 5 Active Campaigns Find up to 300 backlink opportunities per month Advanced AI Website Qualification AI Verified Email Finder Send up to 600 outreach emails per month AI Personalized Email Generation SMTP Integration Initiate Campaigns Full Tracking (opens, replies, and conversions) Campaign Performance Insights Action Choose Growth Scale Plan Price: $199/month Best for: Agencies and high-volume outreach teams. Features 15 Active Campaigns Find up to 1500 backlink opportunities per month Priority AI Website Qualification with smarter matching AI Verified Email Finder Send up to 1500 outreach emails per month Advanced AI Personalized Email Generation SMTP and Gmail Integration Initiate Campaigns Full Tracking and Analytics Dashboard Priority Processing Speed Action Current Plan / Upgrade to Scale Subscription Management The Pricing page enables users to: View current subscription plan Compare all available plans Upgrade to a higher plan Access plan-specific features Monitor campaign and usage limits .",
