        slug: "ai-humanizer",
        title: "AI Humanizer",
        description: "Located in the left navigation menu under the Create section.",
        searchText: "AI Humanizer Located in the left navigation menu under the Create section. Blazly Humanizer helps users transform machine-generated content into natural, engaging, and authentic writing while preserving the original meaning and intent. By analyzing content patterns, sentence structures, and language usage, Blazly Humanizer rewrites content to improve readability, human authenticity, and overall content quality. The feature is designed for marketers, content creators, SEO professionals, and businesses that want content to feel more natural and reader-friendly before publishing. Features Content Editor The Content Editor serves as the primary workspace where users can enter, review, and modify content before analysis and humanization. Users can: Paste existing content. Write content directly within the editor. Edit content before processing. Format content using rich text tools. Prepare content for analysis and rewriting. Rich Text Formatting Blazly Humanizer includes a rich text editor that allows users to structure content while maintaining formatting throughout the humanization process. Supported formatting options include: Bold Italics Underline Strikethrough Hyperlinks H1, H2, H3, and H4 Headings Ordered Lists Unordered Lists Text Alignment Undo and Redo Original Content Tab The Original tab displays the source content provided by the user. This version acts as the baseline for content analysis and humanization. Users can: Review content before processing. Make edits and corrections. Update content before running analysis. Compare the original version with the humanized output. Content Analysis Before content is humanized, Blazly analyzes the submitted text to identify patterns commonly associated with machine-generated content. The analysis evaluates: Sentence structure Language variation Content flow Repetitive phrasing Readability patterns Content authenticity indicators The analysis results help determine areas where content can be improved. Authenticity Score Blazly generates an authenticity score that estimates how natural and human-written the content appears. The score helps users: Understand content quality. Identify machine-generated writing patterns. Measure content improvement after humanization. Evaluate publishing readiness. Humanize Content The Humanize Content feature rewrites the submitted content to improve readability, flow, and authenticity while preserving the original message. During the humanization process, Blazly: Refines sentence structure. Improves language variation. Reduces repetitive wording. Enhances readability. Creates more natural transitions. Improves overall content flow. Preserves the original meaning and context. Humanized Content Tab The Humanized tab displays the rewritten version of the content after processing. Users can: Review the updated content. Compare it with the original version. Make additional edits. Prepare the content for publishing. Copy Content Allows users to instantly copy the humanized content while preserving formatting, making it easy to use across external platforms and content management systems. Save Content Stores both the original and humanized versions of the content, allowing users to revisit, edit, and manage content at a later time. Manual Editing Users retain full control over the final output and can modify any section of the humanized content to match brand guidelines, tone, or publishing requirements.",
